        <h2 class="t-headline-md">8. Cookies Policy</h2>
        <p class="t-body">When you visit our website, we and our third party partners may place small text files called “cookies” and other tracking technologies on your device or browser. When you first visit our website, you will be presented with a cookie consent notice that allows you to accept or decline non-essential cookies. Essential cookies required for the website to function are placed automatically; non-essential cookies, such as analytics and advertising cookies, are placed only after you provide your consent.</p>
